"{\"uid\": \"horseandhound.co.uk-features-olympic-dressage-justina-vanagaite-samuile-lithuanian-rider-866304\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"For a heartwarmingOlympic dressagestory, look no further than Justina Vanagait\\u00e9-Samuile.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 88, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 62, \"end\": 69, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cyprian_and_Justina\", \"score\": 0.9330208168296473, \"rank\": 0.07178529385722207, \"text\": \"Justina\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q43115\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cyprian_and_Justina\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cyprian_and_Justina\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The Lithuanian rider is the first to represent her country at any Olympic equestrian event, and left the arena atParis 2024blowing kisses and waving exuberantly to the cheering crowd.\", \"from\": 89, \"to\": 272, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 163, \"end\": 173, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Equestrianism\", \"score\": 0.9999999999299689, \"rank\": 7.009392499581056e-11, \"text\": \"equestrian\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Equestrianism\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Equestrianism\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It's not just my first Olympics, it's Lithuania's - I am making history!\\\"\", \"from\": 274, \"to\": 348, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 313, \"end\": 322, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lithuania\", \"score\": 0.9888438051117389, \"rank\": 0.01015455586439094, \"text\": \"Lithuania\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lithuania\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lithuania\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"she says.\", \"from\": 349, \"to\": 358, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It does not feel real.\", \"from\": 359, \"to\": 382, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Before my test I was anxious, nervous and happy - everything at once.\", \"from\": 383, \"to\": 452, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I am in shock - in my test I was just trying to do my best, and enjoy my horse, enjoy my ride and enjoy the venue.\", \"from\": 453, \"to\": 567, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The Olympics is crazy.\\\"\", \"from\": 568, \"to\": 591, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Crazier still is Justina's 2,100km road-trip to Paris from Lithuania.\", \"from\": 595, \"to\": 664, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 595, \"end\": 602, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Crazier\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.0083429341021989e-19, \"text\": \"Crazier\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\", \"Q2188189\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Crazier\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Crazier\"}, {\"begin\": 612, \"end\": 619, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cyprian_and_Justina\", \"score\": 0.9330207840329765, \"rank\": 0.07178529385722207, \"text\": \"Justina\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q43115\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cyprian_and_Justina\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cyprian_and_Justina\"}, {\"begin\": 643, \"end\": 648, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999999890861, \"rank\": 1.0721723752054866e-11, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}, {\"begin\": 654, \"end\": 663, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lithuania\", \"score\": 0.9888438051117389, \"rank\": 0.01015455586439094, \"text\": \"Lithuania\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lithuania\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lithuania\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"She herself drove her Olympic ride Nabab to France in the van, taking a friend with her to act as groom.\", \"from\": 665, \"to\": 769, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 700, \"end\": 705, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nabab\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Nabab\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\", \"Q11424\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nabab\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nabab\"}, {\"begin\": 709, \"end\": 715, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"score\": 0.9993003388701182, \"rank\": 0.0006581060265464223, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Our trip took four days,\\\" she says.\", \"from\": 771, \"to\": 807, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"We first stopped at Poznan in Poland, where Nabab rested for 10 hours.\", \"from\": 808, \"to\": 879, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 829, \"end\": 835, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Pozna\\u0144\", \"score\": 0.9994899491136252, \"rank\": 0.0004302468136290841, \"text\": \"Poznan\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Pozna\\u0144\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Pozna\\u0144\"}, {\"begin\": 839, \"end\": 845, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Poland\", \"score\": 0.9994529787133674, \"rank\": 0.00048384733924244325, \"text\": \"Poland\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Poland\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Poland\"}, {\"begin\": 853, \"end\": 858, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nabab\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Nabab\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\", \"Q11424\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nabab\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nabab\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Then we went to another stable in Aachen.\", \"from\": 880, \"to\": 921, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 914, \"end\": 920, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Aachen\", \"score\": 0.9999999686133383, \"rank\": 2.2950212739395073e-08, \"text\": \"Aachen\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Aachen\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Aachen\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He was then meant to stay in Jardy, but I had not booked the box in time and they did not have a spare one, so we stayed in Aachen for one more day.\", \"from\": 922, \"to\": 1070, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1046, \"end\": 1052, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Aachen\", \"score\": 0.9999999686133383, \"rank\": 2.2950212739395073e-08, \"text\": \"Aachen\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Aachen\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Aachen\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"We then left at midnight, drove through the night, and arrived in Versailles at 6am.\", \"from\": 1071, \"to\": 1155, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1137, \"end\": 1147, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Palace_of_Versailles\", \"score\": 0.9999995272556796, \"rank\": 4.727446941341942e-07, \"text\": \"Versailles\", \"types\": [\"Q41176\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Palace_of_Versailles\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Palace_of_Versailles\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"The first day I was thinking, 'Oh, he must be so tired, I will give him four days' rest,\\\" explains Justina, who attended the opening ceremony as one of Lithuania'sflag-bearers.\", \"from\": 1157, \"to\": 1334, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1257, \"end\": 1264, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cyprian_and_Justina\", \"score\": 0.9330207840329765, \"rank\": 0.07178529385722207, \"text\": \"Justina\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q43115\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cyprian_and_Justina\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cyprian_and_Justina\"}, {\"begin\": 1310, \"end\": 1319, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lithuania\", \"score\": 0.9888438051117389, \"rank\": 0.01015455586439094, \"text\": \"Lithuania\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lithuania\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lithuania\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"But when I was lungeing him he was going round and round, snorting like a dragon.\", \"from\": 1335, \"to\": 1417, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The next day he was jumping all over me so I said, 'OK, you feel quite good, I will ride you' - and he was a bit like a dragon.\", \"from\": 1418, \"to\": 1545, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"But I rode him all week without spurs and in a snaffle bridle.\\\"\", \"from\": 1546, \"to\": 1609, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Justina has built up a reputation on social media for having a lot of fun with her precious horse, whom she nicknames Kebab.\", \"from\": 1613, \"to\": 1737, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1613, \"end\": 1620, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cyprian_and_Justina\", \"score\": 0.9330207840329765, \"rank\": 0.07178529385722207, \"text\": \"Justina\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q43115\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cyprian_and_Justina\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cyprian_and_Justina\"}, {\"begin\": 1731, \"end\": 1736, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kebab\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Kebab\", \"types\": [\"Q2095\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kebab\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kebab\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"From one of her final training sessions before the Olympics, she posted a video of her doing pirouettes bareback in a headcollar.\", \"from\": 1738, \"to\": 1867, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I was supposed to be lungeing him, but afterwards I thought maybe I'd just get on and walk, then I started to trot a little bit - and then I thought maybe we can do some movements and do a video,\\\" she says.\", \"from\": 1869, \"to\": 2076, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I am a showgirl,\\\" she adds.\", \"from\": 2078, \"to\": 2106, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"But that does not matter, I still get nervous.\", \"from\": 2107, \"to\": 2154, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I am just happy I managed to hold it together compared with all the riders with so much more experience than me.\\\"\", \"from\": 2155, \"to\": 2268, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Justina scored a creditable 69.20%, which puts her mid-division of the 30 riders to compete on day one of the grand prix qualifier.\", \"from\": 2270, \"to\": 2401, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2270, \"end\": 2277, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cyprian_and_Justina\", \"score\": 0.9330207840329765, \"rank\": 0.07178529385722207, \"text\": \"Justina\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q43115\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cyprian_and_Justina\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cyprian_and_Justina\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"To stay up to date with all the breaking news throughout the Olympic Games, Burghley, the Horse of the Year Show and more,subscribe to the Horse & Hound website  You might also be interested in:              Stay in touch with all the news in the run-up to and throughout the major shows and events during 2025 and beyond with a Horse & Hound subscription.Subscribe todayfor all you need to know ahead of these major events, plus online reports on the action as it happens from our\\u00a0expert team of reporters\\u00a0and in-depth analysis in our special commemorative magazines.\", \"from\": 2403, \"to\": 2971, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2479, \"end\": 2487, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Burghley_Horse_Trials\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.0019829883282241e-18, \"text\": \"Burghley\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Burghley_Horse_Trials\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Burghley_Horse_Trials\"}, {\"begin\": 2542, \"end\": 2555, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Horse_&_Hound\", \"score\": 0.9999999999877218, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Horse & Hound\", \"types\": [\"Q41298\", \"Q386724\", \"Q234460\", \"Q1092563\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Horse_&_Hound\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Horse_&_Hound\"}, {\"begin\": 2732, \"end\": 2745, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Horse_&_Hound\", \"score\": 0.9999999999877218, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Horse & Hound\", \"types\": [\"Q41298\", \"Q386724\", \"Q234460\", \"Q1092563\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Horse_&_Hound\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Horse_&_Hound\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Have a subscription already?Set up your\\u00a0unlimited website access nowThis site is protected by reCAPTCHA and the GooglePrivacy PolicyandTerms of Serviceapply.Show MoreMartha TerryH&H features editorMartha is an experienced journalist who is mad-keen on horses and dogs.\", \"from\": 2972, \"to\": 3240, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Her reporting CV includes the Paris Olympics, European championships, Aachen World Equestrian Festival and World Cup finals.\", \"from\": 3241, \"to\": 3365, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3255, \"end\": 3257, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Curriculum_vitae\", \"score\": 0.9999997394761861, \"rank\": 1.7504584417137621e-07, \"text\": \"CV\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Curriculum_vitae\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Curriculum_vitae\"}, {\"begin\": 3311, \"end\": 3317, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Aachen\", \"score\": 0.9999999686133383, \"rank\": 2.2950212739395073e-08, \"text\": \"Aachen\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Aachen\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Aachen\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"After growing up with assorted liver and white springer spaniels, she enjoyed 14 years with two rescue dogs.\", \"from\": 3366, \"to\": 3474, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Now, her constant companion is Fidget, an extremely energetic and habitually muddy black and white springer.\", \"from\": 3475, \"to\": 3583, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Martha has written on topics as diverse as a top horse's clone to the best GPS trackers for dogs, as well as equestrian and rural matters forCountry Life, The Field, The Times, The SpectatorandThe TelegraphalongsideHorse & Hound.\", \"from\": 3584, \"to\": 3813, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3584, \"end\": 3590, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Martha_Jones\", \"score\": 0.9999999862170627, \"rank\": 1.3634687580460529e-08, \"text\": \"Martha\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Martha_Jones\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Martha_Jones\"}, {\"begin\": 3750, \"end\": 3759, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_Times\", \"score\": 0.9999999399888129, \"rank\": 6.001105845113243e-08, \"text\": \"The Times\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\", \"Q234460\", \"Q11032\", \"Q1092563\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_Times\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_Times\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Stay in touch with all the news in the run-up to and throughout the major shows and events during 2025 and beyond with a Horse & Hound subscription.Subscribe todayfor all you need to know ahead of these major events, plus online reports on the action as it happens from our\\u00a0expert team of reporters\\u00a0and in-depth analysis in our special commemorative magazines.\", \"from\": 3815, \"to\": 4175, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3936, \"end\": 3949, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Horse_&_Hound\", \"score\": 0.9999999999877218, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Horse & Hound\", \"types\": [\"Q41298\", \"Q386724\", \"Q234460\", \"Q1092563\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Horse_&_Hound\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Horse_&_Hound\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Have a subscription already?Set up your\\u00a0unlimited website access now\", \"from\": 4176, \"to\": 4244, \"entities\": []}]}"